{"tid":2110661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"將軍澳隧道轉車站料8月啟用　罕見設男女共用公廁","createTime":"2020-07-16T05:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T06:08:00.000Z","uid":73991,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"46fe87e7930e225128e9ab302035c5c7fafeda62","tid":2110661,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2695000/2696654/123_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2695000%2F2696654%2F123_1024.jpg&h=a41d5391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 西貢區議員獲邀參觀將軍澳隧道巴士轉車站。（秦海城fb）<br />\n將軍澳隧道對出的巴士轉乘站，現正進行工程，據了解該站最快8月啟用，供居民出入時轉車。多名西貢區議員近日獲邀參觀車站，一睹新車站設施。<br />\n<br />\n相片顯示，車站上蓋已經完工，城巴/新巴已豎起路線資訊板及巴士站牌，供日後使用；但九巴則仍未擺放有關顯示板。<br />\n<br />\n至於車站設有傳統公廁，男女分開使用；同時間亦有一個廁格，可供男女共用，並已設計出最新圖標，供市民識認。區議員梁衍忻認為，男女廁共融概念值得一讚，但批評男女廁比例仍追不上時代。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2695000/2696654/123e_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2695000%2F2696654%2F123e_1024.jpg&h=ffdc95d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 香港較鮮見的男女共用公廁。（Zoe Leung 梁衍忻fb）<br />\n<br />\n咪即係殘廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5099850631d8981a724dde64fb2746a947df7c","tid":2110661,"uid":196924,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"最新偷食法<br />\n落車去公廁嚟一炮 之後各自轉車返歸<br />\n神不知鬼不覺<p class=\"center\"></p>"},{"pid":"b85a4617c4d1a889aa04c0fbcad90f203e1b2b32","tid":2110661,"uid":277374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"臭到男女都唔想用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a35ed0069c0810c90c588aa9df955a34666852","tid":2110